campaignTrail_temp.candidate_image_url = "https://i.imgur.com/euKFNNo.png";
campaignTrail_temp.running_mate_image_url = "https://i.imgur.com/r5VWzfc.png";

campaignTrail_temp.multiple_endings = true;
endingPicker = (out, totv, aa, quickstats) => {

    function setImage(url) {
        if(url == '' || url == null) return;
        let interval = setInterval(function () {
            img = document.getElementsByClassName("person_image")[0];
            if (img != null) {
                img.src = url;
                clearInterval(interval);
            }
        }, 50);
    }

    if(quickstats[0] < 110) {
        setImage("https://i.imgur.com/DFVZuyj.png");
        return ` <div style='overflow-y:scroll;height:350px;padding-right:7px'> 
<font size="6"> Sorry! You have lost the 2028 Presidential Elections. </font>
<p>What have you done. The country it's done. You have failed the Democrats, no, the country. This nation is one in decline. You have completely and utterly failed this country. Never show your face around any Democrat again.</p>

<p>Donald Trump has immediately began strengthening his power without having to fear about any Democratic opponents. It was a red tsunami this year, the Democrats are hardly even an opposition party at this point. Donald Trump will take the reigns of this country. Permanently. Within months of his 4th term, Donald Trump has signed several laws that had effectively outlawed the Democratic Party, in response to another assassination attempt on him. </p>

<p>What went wrong during this campaign? In this battle for America, the Democrats certainly were pulverized, but at what point was their fate sealed? Should they really have went through on a true nomination process without Obama? We will never know for certain. What is for certain though is you will never be seen favorably again by anyone considering themselves a liberal. In an entirely winnable election, you have lost, and lost bigly.</p>`;
    }
    if(quickstats[0] < 180) {
        setImage("https://i.imgur.com/6uNkGWL.png");
        return ` <div style='overflow-y:scroll;height:350px;padding-right:7px'> 
<font size="6"> Sorry! You have lost the 2028 Presidential Elections. </font>
<p>In a stunning repudiation of the Democratic Party, you have the lost the election. You have secured a total collapse of the Democratic Party and have allowed the GOP to finally complete their total takeover of the government.</p>
<p></p>
<p>In a sick sort of twisted fate, you have secured even less or about the same amount of Electoral Votes as John McCain- the man you beat in 2008. This is embarassing and will no doubt be what you are remembered for going forward in Democratic circles. You think to yourself though, this can't be your fault. You're Barack Obama, the most popular politician, the only explanation is a complete disintegration from the Democrats in the American electorate, something you could not fix despite being believed you could.</p>

<p>The only saving grace for this election is the fact that the Republicans have not reached a supermajority in either the House or Senate, but their majority is still yuuuge. The Democrats can only hope to fillibuster anything the Republicans try to pass, but some are concerned Trump will declare martial law to force his agenda through and become a comfortable dictator.</p>

<p>Following the election you and your family would leave the United States, out of fear of the political witch hunt which Donald Trump has orchestrated against you. You land in Indonesia where you're given a warm reception, it's a pretty nice place to live in exile. Although you probably won't get to live in peace and quiet, you'll always have to worry about Trump sending spies to go and assassinate you. It's Joever.</p>
`;
    }
    if(quickstats[0] < 218) {
        setImage("https://i.imgur.com/vQ2xrtv.png");
        return ` <div style='overflow-y:scroll;height:350px;padding-right:7px'> 
<font size="6">Sorry! You have lost the 2028 Presidential Elections. </font>

<p></p>prompt: "make a paragraph about how Obama felt after losing the 2028 election to donald trump"
<p></p>
<p>"Well, folks, let me tell you—Obama, after losing the 2028 election to Donald Trump, probably sat there thinking, "How did this happen?" Sad! He likely reflected on what went wrong, folks. But here’s the thing, nobody campaigns like Trump. Nobody brings energy to the people like Trump. So, while Obama might’ve been disappointed, you know, deep down, even he knows: MAGA is unstoppable. Believe me."</p>
<p></p>
<p>An incredible poetic piece written in the perspective of Donald Trump, for some reason. (Note this was the ONLY use of AI in this thing, just a small thing for 1 specific ending.)</p>`;
    }
    if(quickstats[0] == 270) {
        setImage("https://i.imgur.com/YaC3QeO.png");
        return ` <div style='overflow-y:scroll;height:350px;padding-right:7px'> 
<font size="6"> Sorry! You have lost the 2028 Presidential Elections. </font>
<p>After all of this, the Democrats have once again lost the election. </p>
<p> </p>
<p>After winning 270 Electoral Votes, Donald Trump went on a campaign of trying to overturn the election results which would delay the certification of some electors for a few weeks. However, some states would still count them on their regularly scheduled time. The electoral came in and it was a shock to the nation. 2 electors from Massachusetts would cast their electoral votes for Donald J. Trump and J.D Vance. </p>

<p>It had finally happened. Somebody winning the election through faithless electors. The Democrats were furious, Obama refused to accept the outcome and called upon Democratic strongholds in the North East and West Coast to threaten secession unless Congress passed several laws which would favor Democrat election chances along with eliminating the Electoral College.</p>
<p></p>
<p>The Republican controlled Congress ignored the demands of the Democratic states and starting with Vermont, 10 states from the North East and West Coast would secede from the Union. What followed were tense negotiations by both sides to attempt to amend the issues between the 2 nations. The talks would collapse as Donald Trump refused to concede and demanded he stay as President for the next 4 years.</p>`;
    }
    if(quickstats[0] == 226) {
        setImage("https://i.imgur.com/XU9Wy59.png");
        return ` <div style='overflow-y:scroll;height:350px;padding-right:7px'> 

<font size="6"> Sorry! You have lost the 2028 Presidential Elections. </font>
